configuration:
instance.volumes
comma separated list of URIs for volumes. example: hdfs://localhost:9000/accumulo
instance.zookeeper.host localhost:2181 comma separated list of zookeeper servers
instance.secret DEFAULT A secret unique to a given instance that all servers must know in order to communicate with one another. Change it before initialization. To change it later use ./bin/accumulo org.apache.accumulo.server.util.ChangeSecret --old [oldpasswd] --new [newpasswd], and then update this file.
